{"tid":862964,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"換車問題：舊車牌轉去新車，舊車抽新number","createTime":"2018-10-15T09:18:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T01:42:42.000Z","uid":77811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a0c58a2efbb5bbad4378abcf0b36225042fc1018","tid":862964,"uid":77811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T09:18:18.000Z","msg":"（交易前）<br />\n舊車A: 車牌AA1111<br />\n新車B: 車牌BB2222<br />\n<br />\n（交易後）<br />\n舊車A: 車牌CC3333<br />\n新車B: 車牌AA1111<br />\n<br />\n想請教吓巴絲打點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 問賣家拎牌簿copy果時同保險講會出落AA1111？<br />\n<br />\n2. 咁舊車要到時抽牌先知個新number，會出新牌簿CC3333？<br />\n<br />\n3. 再拎新牌簿copy (CC3333) 俾保險公司出cover note再買牌費？"},{"pid":"69b618daaa64a26f8c723279f2a4628609aed38b","tid":862964,"uid":77811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba1896e7a023a6ff806aa20805cebd01909d72c","tid":862964,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"BB2222先過咗去你名下, 你先至可以將AA1111套落去B車..."},{"pid":"c263e70bb95f81da413fc5081df8f3daa2817571","tid":862964,"uid":77811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ba1896e7a023a6ff806aa20805cebd01909d72c","tid":862964,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T10:31:54.000Z","msg":"BB2222先過咗去你名下, 你先至可以將AA1111套落去B車..."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:22:33.000Z","msg":"即係要好似平時買二手車咁出cover note再過好晒戶<br />\n之後再做套牌同抽新牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c690dc12c8c11f20ece6047d3d4a638196c63a","tid":862964,"uid":7758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T23:48:05.000Z","msg":"幫新車抽number 先<br />\n然後兩架車做交換車牌手續<br />\n<br />\n利申:聽個f